description: The local militia patrols the base of the impressive inner wall of the keep which dominates the northern section of the grassy sward.  Under the watchful eyes of the nearby guards, enterprising merchants have set up tents and various stands to sell goods to the locals who come here in search of good sales during the day.

title: [Guardian Keep, Inner Wall]
